nitionrobotics/ign-transport/pull-requests/254/_/diff#comment-52617883"}}, "parent": {"id": 52616659, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pullrequests/254/comments/52616659.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pull-requests/254/_/diff#comment-52616659"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 254, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pullrequests/254.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pull-requests/254"}}, "title": "Do not overwrite LD_LIBRARY_PATH"}, "content": {"raw": "That's understandable, since Windows isn't nearly as accommodating towards command line tools.\n\nIt seems that at some point we may be able to leverage CPack to generate `.msi` package installers for Windows, which should make it more feasible to fully support `ign` on Windows. But that's probably a conversation for another time and place.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>That's understandable, since Windows isn't nearly as accommodating towards command line tools.</p>\n<p>It seems that at some point we may be able to leverage CPack to generate <code>.msi</code> package installers for Windows, which should make it more feasible to fully support <code>ign</code> on Windows. But that's probably a conversation for another time and place.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-12-26T17:41:03.076047+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "updated_on": "2017-12-26T17:41:03.078567+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 52617883}, "pull_request": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 254, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pullrequests/254.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pull-requests/254"}}, "title": "Do not overwrite LD_LIBRARY_PATH"}}, {"comment": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pullrequests/254/comments/52616659.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pull-requests/254/_/diff#comment-52616659"}}, "parent": {"id": 52616286, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pullrequests/254/comments/52616286.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pull-requests/254/_/diff#comment-52616286"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 254, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pullrequests/254.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pull-requests/254"}}, "title": "Do not overwrite LD_LIBRARY_PATH"}, "content": {"raw": "I don't think `ign` works on Windows for now.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I don't think <code>ign</code> works on Windows for now.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-12-26T16:57:53.418853+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Carlos Ag\u00fcero", "uuid": "{da8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bda8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bda8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/692bf15758111acaddae4da15a47f9e5d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsCA-0.png"}}, "nickname": "caguero", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:4ded1ddf-947e-4154-bbd1-3dba24f1bdbd"}, "updated_on": "2017-12-26T16:57:53.421080+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 52616659}, "pull_request": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 254, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pullrequests/254.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pull-requests/254"}}, "title": "Do not overwrite LD_LIBRARY_PATH"}}, {"comment": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pullrequests/254/comments/52616286.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pull-requests/254/_/diff#comment-52616286"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 254, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pullrequests/254.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pull-requests/254"}}, "title": "Do not overwrite LD_LIBRARY_PATH"}, "content": {"raw": "Has this issue been tested on Windows? I imagine we'll face similar problems, especially when compiling in Visual Studio (as opposed to `nmake`), because Visual Studio uses a multi-configuration generator for CMake. That means the location of the binary won't be known at configuration time, and we would need to use generator expressions to determine the value of `IGN_TEST_LIBRARY_PATH`. You can find an example [here](#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/src/923f816153a72e8eb28574bf5a1ce7f575c9bcef/test/util/CMakeLists.txt?at=default&fileviewer=file-view-default) in `ign-common` for the dummy plugins. It's not a pretty solution, so suggestions for more elegant solutions are very welcome.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Has this issue been tested on Windows? I imagine we'll face similar problems, especially when compiling in Visual Studio (as opposed to <code>nmake</code>), because Visual Studio uses a multi-configuration generator for CMake. That means the location of the binary won't be known at configuration time, and we would need to use generator expressions to determine the value of <code>IGN_TEST_LIBRARY_PATH</code>. You can find an example <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-common/src/923f816153a72e8eb28574bf5a1ce7f575c9bcef/test/util/CMakeLists.txt?at=default&amp;fileviewer=file-view-default\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a> in <code>ign-common</code> for the dummy plugins. It's not a pretty solution, so suggestions for more elegant solutions are very welcome.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2017-12-26T16:45:32.032496+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9/d42d74cf-c1bd-4431-8288-07f543bbe325/128"}}, "nickname": "mxgrey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:67759e29-d1df-465f-868d-047738e36fc9"}, "updated_on": "2017-12-26T16:45:32.035993+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 52616286}, "pull_request": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 254, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pullrequests/254.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pull-requests/254"}}, "title": "Do not overwrite LD_LIBRARY_PATH"}}, {"approval": {"date": "2017-12-26T16:39:13.496915+00:00", "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 254, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pullrequests/254.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-transport/pull-requests/254"}}, "title": "Do not overwrite LD_LIBRARY_PATH"}, "user": {"display_name": "Michael Grey", "uuid": "{c1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-474c-ae99-72fdc53a59c9%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc1cdfe52-2887-47